Wishlist for features of Xbox Series X:
1. Full Keyboard and mouse support for all Xbox games. Hoping we can use USB wired Keyboard and Mouse for all Xbox games without using any third party
adapters(e.g. XIM APEX, CronusMax) and also able to use wireless Keyboard and Mouse too for all Xbox games.

3. Ease of use for Secure Cloud Storage Backup and External Backup for Installed Games.
